  i .delete() is used without .where(). This will delete all rows in the table.
  
    3 │ // simple delete without where
  > 4 │ await db.delete(users);
      │       ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
    5 │ await nested.db.delete(users);
    6 │ await context.nested.db.delete(users);
  
  i Add a .where() clause to delete only the intended rows, or use .where(sql`1=1`) to explicitly delete all rows.
  
  i This rule belongs to the nursery group, which means it is not yet stable and may change in the future. Visit https://biomejs.dev/linter/#nursery for more information.
  

